# NETWORK::FADE_OUT_LOCAL_PLAYER

## Summary
Fades out the local player locally and remotely

## Parameters
* **BOOL** fadeOut:
If true, set player fading out.
If false the fade out is removed and the player will be immediately visible again

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Hardcoded to not work in SP.
